## Education

**Doctor's degree in Informatics, (2016-2018)**
- Kyoto University, Japan. Supervisorl Prof. Shohei Nobuhara. The title of my doctor thesis is **Camera Calibration Based on Mirror Reflections**.

**Master's degree in Informatics, (2010-2012)**
- Kyoto University, Japan. Supervisor; Prof. Takashi Matsuyama. The title of my master thesis is **Mirror-based Camera Pose Estimation Using an Orthogonality Constraint**.

**Bachelor's degree in Engineering, (2006-2010)**
- Kyoto University, Japan. Supervisor; Prof. Minoh Michihiko. The title of my bachelor thesis is **Display Visual and Auditory Information to Support Manipulation of Virtual Object in Virtual Studio**.



